Package com.commander4j.db

Class JDBWasteLog

java.lang.Object
com.commander4j.db.JDBWasteLog
public class JDBWasteLog extends Object
The JDBWasteLog class updates the table APP_WASTE_LOG. This table contains a single row for each unique Waste Location as stored in the APP_WASTE_LOG table.
